[SHORT DESC]
10% chance to freeze the target. 10% chance to flinch the target.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Deals damage. Has a 10% chance to freeze the target. Has a 10% chance to flinch the target.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Ice Fang has an exceedingly low Base Power, and is usually outclassed by Ice Punch. Pokemon that cannot learn Ice Punch may use this move for coverage, the best example being Gliscor.</p>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/ice_punch">Ice Punch</a> is a more powerful option.</p>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/icicle_crash">Icicle Crash</a> is a more powerful option with less accuracy.</p>